div.head: Description of changes for 2012.10
div.p: This is the first public version of this text. It is a first draft created froma copy of the descriptive transcription of the St. Victor manuscript. Corrections and additions still need to be made and are pending a collation comparision of the available manuscript witnesses. A transcription of the Sorbonne manuscriopt still needs to be completed. Unclear items have been tagged and most name elements have been given a unique reference. Citations, cross-references, and a critical apparatus still need to be constructed"
